---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import rightArrow from "../images/icons/right-arrow.webp";
import logo from "../images/shared/logo.webp";
import rainbowBgFlipped from "../images/shared/rainbow-bg-bw-flipped.webp";
---

<div
  class="relative block w-full bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat shadow shadow-test"
>
  <Image
    src={rainbowBgFlipped}
    class="-z-10 opacity-[75] absolute w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
    alt="logo"
  />
  <div class="px-6 py-12">
    <div class="m-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-extrabold">
        CYPHER Queenz began in 2019...
      </h2>
      <div
        class="mb-12 flex flex-col justify-evenly gap-12 sm:flex-row sm:gap-2"
      >
        <div class="flex-1 rounded p-1 shadow-test">
          <p class="rounded bg-skin-base p-4 text-xl">
            ... after many years of seeing a need for more community for Bgirls.
            We give props to all the Bgirls who have been holding it down for a
            long time, but have observed many women briefly coming into the
            scene and then quickly leaving because of lack of support. There is
            an explosion of talented Bgirls all over the world now and there is
            so much more to come. In Seattle, we want to provide that space for
            them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="basis-1/3 px-12">
          <Image
            src={logo}
            class="object-contain h-full object-center drop-shadow-xl"
            alt="Cypher Queenz Logo"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="relative bottom-0 m-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-evenly rounded-full border border-gray-900 bg-skin-base p-5 px-6 text-center text-2xl shadow-test transition-all duration-150 hover:bottom-2 sm:flex-row"
      >
        <span>
          Read more about our
          <span style="font-variant:small-caps;" class="text-3xl font-extrabold"
            >mission</span
          >,
          <span style="font-variant:small-caps;" class="text-3xl font-extrabold"
            >vision</span
          > and
          <span style="font-variant:small-caps;" class="text-3xl font-extrabold"
            >values</span
          >
        </span>
        <Image src={rightArrow} class="w-12 h-full" alt="Right arrow icon" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
